{"type":"issue.created","timestamp":"2026-06-09T16:55:47.323Z","actor":"ikey","issueId":"manta-e230","issue":{"title":"Fix add() to handle string inputs correctly","description":"add(a, b) uses the + operator, so string inputs concatenate instead of summing (e.g. add('2', '3') returns '23' rather than 5). Coerce arguments to numbers before adding, or validate that both inputs are numbers.","status":"open","priority":"p1","issueType":"bug","assignee":null,"createdAt":"2026-06-09T16:55:47.323Z","createdBy":"ikey","updatedAt":"2026-06-09T16:55:47.323Z","updatedBy":"ikey"}}
